Program: Outlook
Title: Money Trouble at the Hague
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr6b
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The former International Court for Justice in the Hague is in financial difficulties because of an increase in the cases it has. Why rising living standards in Delhi are bad news for taxi drivers there, and, celebrating telescopes on the 400th anniversary of the instrument which changed the way we see the cosmos. Show less